    public static class MultiColumnRestriction.InWithValues
extends SingleColumnRestriction.InWithValues
implements MultiColumnRestriction.IN
    An IN restriction that has a set of terms for in values. For example: "SELECT ... WHERE (a, b, c) IN ((1, 2, 3), (4, 5, 6))" or "WHERE (a, b, c) IN (?, ?)"
